# Code owners for this repository.
#
# Branch protection on main enables "Require review from Code Owners"; that
# rule is a no-op without this file. The final matching pattern wins, so the
# catch-all below makes the owner a required reviewer on every pull request.
#
# Add more specific rules above the catch-all to route sensitive paths to
# additional reviewers, e.g.:
#   /policy/                 @jaricsng @security-team
#   /.github/workflows/      @jaricsng @security-team

*                            @jaricsng

# Security-sensitive surfaces call out the owner explicitly so intent is
# clear even if the catch-all is ever narrowed.
/.github/                    @jaricsng
/policy/                     @jaricsng
/scripts/                    @jaricsng
/Dockerfile                  @jaricsng
